TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: This is the Accelerated Invoicing indicator (ITPR008033, 8/2014).and is used to isolate a group of claims (typically the 1st, 2nd, and approx 1/2 of the 3rd month of a quarter) for input to Invoicing. This is an attempt to keep that isolated group of claims from changing to prevent the results of the invoice run changing due to claims being added or removed.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: CLM_PREVW_IND

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: This is an Aetna only field representing their RX Plan ID value. The source of this field is the CDD data on EDW. Represents many distinct data elements needed to define the adjudication of a claim at CVS.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: RX_PLAN_ID

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: This is an Aenta only field representing a list of GPIs and/or NDCs that that require a precertification approval from the clinical area before the drug can be dispensed.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: PCERT_DRUG_LIST_NM

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: This is an Aetna only field representing a list of Non Preferred drugs that require the member to try other drugs for the same therapy before the restricted drug can be dispensed.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: STEP_THRPY_DRUG_LIST_NM

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: This is an Aetna only field that defines quantity of medication a member can get for a given day supply based off of dosage guidelines, or other clinical considerations.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: QTY_LMT_DRUG_LIST_NM

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: This is an Aetna only field representing the state which a plan sponsor contract is written. This is not the same as resident state.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: CTRC_ST_CD

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: This is an Aetna only field, populated for Aetnas Z clms which indicate a Medicare Part B claim when it is determined that drug is Med B; also for Aetnas I clms processed through a pharmacy to RxCLAIM but is covered under the mbrs medical benefit.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: MED_PYBL_CD
